# init(sequence:)

**Initializer**

Creates a feature value that contains a sequence.

## Declaration

```swift
convenience init(sequence: MLSequence)
```

## Parameters

- **sequence**: An [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLSequence] instance.

## Creating collection feature values

- **init(dictionary:)**: Creates a feature value that contains a dictionary of numbers.
